  "id": "RAW_27a729",
  "title": "从开源项目到 2500 万美元融资：如何打造下一代 AI Agent 的互联网基础设施",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3NDc2MjQxMg==&mid=2247489122&idx=1&sn=10bdfe967dbb3ac981890ecfe59fa782",
  "date": "2025-08-11 02:05:00",
